PrecisApproval of the appointment by the Minister of Transport of ROBERT H. HILL, of Prince Rupert, British Columbia, as a director of the board of directors of the Prince Rupert Port Corporation to hold office during pleasure for a term of one year, in the place of Douglas Edward Moore, whose term has expired.
